Name: Lilley
Description:
The Division of Lilley consists of:

  • part of the Brisbane City Council, and
  • part of the Moreton Bay Regional Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: The area is mostly residential but includes Brisbane's domestic and international airports, light and heavy engineering, sea-cargo facilities, chemical production, warehousing (civilian and military), oil refining and storage and various small industries.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Sir Charles Lilley, 1827-97, Premier of Queensland (1868-70), member of the Queensland Parliament (1860-74) and responsible for introducing free education into Queensland.
